{"tid":806908,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【突然收水】彭博：人行8月定向正回購3,000億","createTime":"2018-09-05T06:10:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T11:37:00.000Z","uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"395c05c00b25fab291ed5471185d15b42af0d7a9","tid":806908,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T06:10:41.000Z","msg":"《彭博》引述不具名知情人士指出，為把好貨幣供給總閘門，保持流動性合理充裕，中國人民銀行8月向數家大型銀行進行了定向正回購操作，回收流動性總規模約為3,000億元人民幣。根據目前信息，此為人行逾三年來首次通過正回購回籠流動性。<br />\n<br />\n知情人士並稱，向一家國有銀行操作的定向正回購期限為7天。其中一位知情人士表示，短期限操作是為了方便到期後及時釋放流動性，以支持此後的地方債發行。目前尚不清楚此次定向正回購的所有期限。"},{"pid":"83ed3963f885065377153edfab7a078112f3bc54","tid":806908,"uid":122377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T06:49:26.000Z","msg":"中國都收水啦"},{"pid":"b943ee3aa60c2f71fa5d55acc593dfc90aeaf045","tid":806908,"uid":106810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83ed3963f885065377153edfab7a078112f3bc54","tid":806908,"uid":122377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T06:49:26.000Z","msg":"中國都收水啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T06:55:14.000Z","msg":"黎緊咪又發萬億債，幾千億有咩意思"},{"pid":"229efd7cc8a9bba947f983c60428c10cad1bff64","tid":806908,"uid":58413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T07:31:55.000Z","msg":"乜撚野叫做&ldquo;把好貨幣供給總閘&rdquo;"},{"pid":"5420a43a83f16b3bacb01138c8c788b6da28cd11","tid":806908,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T08:37:54.000Z","msg":"進退失據 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ca172957aee5552e6db28c6a136cc89007d0b7","tid":806908,"uid":182475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T08:39:52.000Z","msg":"有無人解釋下佢點解會左右互搏？"},{"pid":"bdca051540c19a6a08436b57f5cee52965dbd0f9","tid":806908,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02ca172957aee5552e6db28c6a136cc89007d0b7","tid":806908,"uid":182475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-